            <h4>UI Client Code Architecture</h4>
            <p>
                The UI architecture of the application is based on MVVM model.
                 I have used Bootstrap library for design. I have also used Knockout JS library as View Model to fetch data from server side and also Clientside validation using Knockout Js.
                 As we connect to server, it response back with JSON result, which makes the application quicker and faster in execution.
            </p>
            <h4>Server Code Architecture</h4>
<p>The server side code architecture is based in Domain Driven Design Architecture. The Domain (logic) of application is separated in Service part.
             The Database part is separated in Data part. The database is code first approach. I have used entity Framework 6 to interact with database. There is repository pattern while accessing database. The Model (entity) is separated in Model part. And the web part is also separately kept. The Web part is based in MVC architecture.
</p>
